\fs[19]\c[19]\ow[0]October 5th 2016
\fb
Worried about how your tuition money is being spent? The SDU board of directors takes in to consideration your feedback when choosing renovation projects.
<wordwrap>\fs[19]\c[19]\ow[0]

At ESU, renovation money is wasted on extravagant construction equipment. Just last week we spotted a tanker truck at the campus. A contractor? No! It was purchased by ESU for irrigation purposes but has remained unused, as far as we could tell.
